nsions, unbalances (such as differences between BL healing power and Mage/Nec healing powers) should be fixed now and ported over to Oow after that<br>2- Every class will get better, which means that the gaps won't get any shorter between classes, in fact they'll more than likely become wider in absolute values (if they don't change in relative values)
